-- Cipla Says Report of Chief Executive Lulla Stepping Down Are `Speculative'
-- Adi Narayan
-- 2010-07-09T06:04:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-09/cipla-says-report-of-chief-executive-officer-stepping-down-speculative-.html

          
          
             Cipla Ltd. said news report about its
chief executive leaving the company is “speculative.”  
 The executive Amar Lulla is on medical leave, it said in a
statement to the Bombay Stock Exchange today.  
